    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>292968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_040_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>うわっ……っと、おまえ……
あいつらの仲間か！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Woah! ...Are you friends
with those circus freaks!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_040_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我が名はフラムベルク、
この塔の守護者</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I am Flamberge, the protector
of this tower.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293136</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_040_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『不燃の古木』を奪った
貴様らの罪、我が剣にて裁く！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You who have stolen away the
"Unburnable Tree" shall be judged
for your sin by this sword!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293212</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_040_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ちょっ……な、何を……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wai...Wh-WHAT...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293296</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_040_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>それはわたしたちじゃありません！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We aren't the ones you seek!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>293384</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_260_040_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>言い訳は無用！
死ぬがいい！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your excuses are worthless!
Prepare to die!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
